{"tid":156801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家人不思進取回曬塘點搞","createTime":"2017-03-15T04:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T09:11:24.000Z","uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d97cf451f4bbdf6fe079103d8d6b3863aa8a2a1d","tid":156801,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"本身我父母就係靠自己打拼唔係大家族來<br />\n咁佢地以前係大陸經濟初初發展個時就番去炒樓<br />\n多年來投資炒賣<br />\n最後宜家成果就係香港2個單位<br />\n大陸2個半(半間親戚夾份)，都係一線城市既普通樓啦<br />\n同有一筆人仔，唔多可能百零萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁呢幾年佢地開始過退休生活<br />\n大陸既物業2間租客無租後就丟空無再打理<br />\n1間話得閒自己上去渡假用<br />\n舊人仔就咁做定期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒就去旅行不理世事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就話不如我來打理啦<br />\n同埋試下放一間半間出去筆錢番來做首期又好買劏房什至車位都好啦<br />\n同埋舊錢做定期不如買收息股<br />\n點知佢地又話d錢拎唔到番來無謂搞咁多<br />\n離曬地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔俾我去打理又唔聽人講<br />\n我宜家就日日做份頹工無發圍<br />\n家人就回曬塘咁咩都唔想搞浪費曬d資產<br />\n搞到有機會上流都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔明佢地諗咩<br />\n大家呢種情況會點勸佢地<br />\n真心想脫離奴隸階層有下自己事業都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32d8e01747e43e7b6f7927bfa5254623c225951","tid":156801,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"你老豆老母有錢 關你個死廢青乜野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12c2da626cbf06f897b8ab05fadecc73fba7c47","tid":156801,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆老母有錢 關你個死廢青乜野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住幫佢地善用資產姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f1c7ac3fc0104ff9a4729d04b4f628c523aa7a","tid":156801,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"你老豆老母啲錢關你撚事呀？"},{"pid":"4828a6b1d506e62091722c51e4420ce197162d09","tid":156801,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆老母有錢 關你個死廢青乜野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地死左你咪有錢啦囉"},{"pid":"3c40d374566226c0184b2ee886d43ac735c483c8","tid":156801,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"75941062972890aa6717b5546f4ecbf391932851","tid":156801,"uid":82113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"好仔不論爺田地， 好女不論嫁妝衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f17fc1ea112ff7bb86b29725421d73cf16f74","tid":156801,"uid":5293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你老豆老母有錢 關你個死廢青乜野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住幫佢地善用資產姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪又係想用屋企人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 好撚葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2448e1172b69ade51fb71ed850adc4d81a8d3d","tid":156801,"uid":3876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"孝順下父母<br />\n日日食3高1低"},{"pid":"3ac42ecc89fe477e17ea77fd9407cae853d29720","tid":156801,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孝順下父母<br />\n日日食3高1低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無你咁仆街"},{"pid":"9cca291bebfa0d57c622e27088ff2babfe6218eb","tid":156801,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa