: red;\">唔</span>養你哋，你哋好慘嫁！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5da7bcc28eca25eaad3aa69dc87e3e0de455e167","tid":156801,"uid":32150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ec1c4be0dfe1a6c5a9ced03fc2cf88c0166407cd","tid":156801,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"炒就炒啦,投你老母資咩"},{"pid":"3f783ed267bac6db2d2e49065bc60b7e0197956e","tid":156801,"uid":7641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"反省下 寧願蝕都唔比你打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5715541029aad82fdafcd49e8f21e33e103a115d","tid":156801,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"你父母d棺材本關你鬼事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時佢地百年歸老變左鬼就真係關你事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19750ab2c5b665e74a9109c237e88b2d3aa9f0ae","tid":156801,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"有得睇無得洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我屋企個d係有租出去，有得洗"},{"pid":"30aefa7bb39ebec4bc4c1b0f1cc02ef9123014dc","tid":156801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"仲以為移民回流，原來吼住人d錢"},{"pid":"e070fcb9cd4d127ddb71ffe0c8e304e35430f8ff","tid":156801,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"正廢柴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n襯後生係好應該靠自己努力"},{"pid":"4a2af70cf9c9a87682e74c35f69b015332b6371d","tid":156801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁多人唔生仔"},{"pid":"f8d1f87357cc6801917f086ec367c563812d2a5b","tid":156801,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我宜家就日日做份頹工無發圍</span><br />\n家人就回曬塘咁咩都唔想搞浪費曬d資產<br />\n搞到有機會上流都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔明佢地諗咩<br />\n大家呢種情況會點勸佢地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真心想脫離奴隸階層有下自己事業都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事實係樓主有個有眼光有米既家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但樓主就普通人一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以就想拎家人d財產做投資+收租，但係樓主d家人唔幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就話人不思進取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8989b1acfe3b1d34f637d784a6408b37fff82190","tid":156801,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"老母老豆不思進取都整到4層樓返黎<br />\n你呢樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f79cf667ace2fb95cb0c3d9d4e1a5e5c4347f7","tid":156801,"uid":9899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"我宜家就日日做份頹工無發圍<br />\n<br />\n廢就廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbc1e98b049d0eb7753f18b0b6e3ab3b07bb9ae","tid":156801,"uid":49603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"你老豆老母識諗過你啦"},{"pid":"dbdbe1135a2af8218a28bfdd2aadace2ecc7671b","tid":156801,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係叫上咗岸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老實實啲野佢哋嘅，鍾意點處理都冇問題<br />\n你想發圍咪靠自己<br />\n失敗咗至少餓你唔死